[
  {
    "text": "I wasn't always the great and terrible",
    "start": 0.4,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "entity.",
    "start": 3.439,
    "duration": 5.681
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I had a mother and a father as all",
    "start": 5.44,
    "duration": 6.319
  },
  {
    "text": "children do. He's hatching. He's really",
    "start": 9.12,
    "duration": 5.639
  },
  {
    "text": "hatching.",
    "start": 11.759,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Mama, Papa?",
    "start": 16.0,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Our beautiful son. Welcome to your new",
    "start": 18.32,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "home.",
    "start": 21.439,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Home?",
    "start": 22.48,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": ">> That's right, son. Now, come take a look",
    "start": 23.439,
    "duration": 5.121
  },
  {
    "text": "at your kingdom.",
    "start": 25.76,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "Critters of the Winter Kingdom, behold",
    "start": 28.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "the Owl Prince.",
    "start": 31.279,
    "duration": 4.001
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I was royalty.",
    "start": 33.12,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "My parents made sure that everyone knew",
    "start": 35.28,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": "it.",
    "start": 38.32,
    "duration": 7.88
  },
  {
    "text": "They had such high expectations for me.",
    "start": 40.719,
    "duration": 5.481
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Stay low, son. The wolf hasn't spotted",
    "start": 51.6,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "us yet.",
    "start": 54.399,
    "duration": 6.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I will, Dad. This is fun.",
    "start": 55.6,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Fun isn't the point.",
    "start": 62.079,
    "duration": 4.041
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We, as our royalty, are at the very top",
    "start": 68.88,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "of the food chain. Sometimes we must",
    "start": 71.52,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "remind the other alphas of this.",
    "start": 73.76,
    "duration": 5.999
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You mean you want me to kill it?",
    "start": 76.08,
    "duration": 8.679
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Of course. Now, on you go.",
    "start": 79.759,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Good doggy. Nice doggy.",
    "start": 89.92,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Get on with it, boy.",
    "start": 95.68,
    "duration": 7.399
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I I can't.",
    "start": 98.799,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 103.3,
    "duration": 3.109
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh,",
    "start": 108.64,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, help me.",
    "start": 110.72,
    "duration": 6.359
  },
  {
    "text": "Such a weakling.",
    "start": 113.68,
    "duration": 3.399
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No, don't abandon me.",
    "start": 117.439,
    "duration": 4.761
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't stop. Please",
    "start": 124.479,
    "duration": 5.881
  },
  {
    "text": ">> leave him alone.",
    "start": 126.719,
    "duration": 3.641
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 139.82,
    "duration": 4.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 141.76,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Son,",
    "start": 152.48,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> are you okay?",
    "start": 156.239,
    "duration": 5.601
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Honey, no. What have you done?",
    "start": 158.08,
    "duration": 7.439
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It isn't his fault. Take care of our",
    "start": 161.84,
    "duration": 6.679
  },
  {
    "text": "son.",
    "start": 165.519,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 169.27,
    "duration": 2.81
  },
  {
    "text": "on love.",
    "start": 170.4,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": ">> My father never forgave me for that day.",
    "start": 172.08,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "To honor my mother's dying wish, he",
    "start": 174.959,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "spared my life. But he had a plan to",
    "start": 177.68,
    "duration": 5.839
  },
  {
    "text": "make me pay all the same.",
    "start": 180.959,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Where are we going, Dad?",
    "start": 183.519,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": ">> The Frog Kingdom. As you can see,",
    "start": 187.04,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "they've overstepped their boundaries.",
    "start": 188.879,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time to make a deal to end this",
    "start": 190.72,
    "duration": 5.48
  },
  {
    "text": "feud once and for all.",
    "start": 192.319,
    "duration": 3.881
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah, the Owl King. To what do I owe the",
    "start": 203.76,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "pleasure?",
    "start": 207.76,
    "duration": 3.119
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I think we both know our two kingdoms",
    "start": 208.8,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "have been getting awfully close lately.",
    "start": 210.879,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes, the great frog kingdom expands",
    "start": 214.0,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "every day.",
    "start": 217.519,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I'd rather us not be enemies.",
    "start": 219.36,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh, and what will you offer me to keep",
    "start": 222.08,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "the peace?",
    "start": 225.12,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "My son.",
    "start": 228.0,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What?",
    "start": 229.68,
    "duration": 3.119
  },
  {
    "text": ">> He will become your personal servant,",
    "start": 230.48,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "courtesy of the Owl Kingdom.",
    "start": 232.799,
    "duration": 7.601
  },
  {
    "text": ">> This is a most gracious offer, Owl King.",
    "start": 235.76,
    "duration": 7.64
  },
  {
    "text": "However,",
    "start": 240.4,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> what?",
    "start": 244.879,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Why bother with a pawn when the king is",
    "start": 246.08,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "ripe for the taking?",
    "start": 249.68,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 251.68,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You This is your fault. Everything is",
    "start": 253.28,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "your fault.",
    "start": 256.16,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "See him?",
    "start": 260.72,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": ">> In his grief over my mother's death, my",
    "start": 272.56,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "father tried to get rid of me for good.",
    "start": 276.08,
    "duration": 7.399
  },
  {
    "text": "And he paid the price.",
    "start": 279.28,
    "duration": 4.199
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I had nothing. No one. I was completely",
    "start": 284.32,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": "alone",
    "start": 288.32,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "until",
    "start": 289.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Are you all right?",
    "start": 293.199,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "Leave me alone.",
    "start": 296.08,
    "duration": 7.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, it's okay. I'm the deer. What's",
    "start": 299.28,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "your name?",
    "start": 303.12,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I'm the owl. Uh,",
    "start": 304.639,
    "duration": 6.881
  },
  {
    "text": "just the owl will do. These woods are",
    "start": 308.639,
    "duration": 5.521
  },
  {
    "text": "scary all alone. I could really use a",
    "start": 311.52,
    "duration": 8.32
  },
  {
    "text": "friend if you want one. That is",
    "start": 314.16,
    "duration": 8.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll be your friend. Yeah. All right.",
    "start": 319.84,
    "duration": 8.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on. Try to keep up. Hey, wait.",
    "start": 323.12,
    "duration": 8.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> The deer and I became close like",
    "start": 328.639,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "brothers. He taught me how to hunt, not",
    "start": 331.44,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "just for pride, but for food. He",
    "start": 334.56,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "respected nature and didn't strive to",
    "start": 337.6,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "rule over it, but to protect it. He was",
    "start": 340.88,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "everything I wanted to be. But something",
    "start": 344.4,
    "duration": 6.239
  },
  {
    "text": "inside me stirred",
    "start": 347.44,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "you. This is your fault. Everything is",
    "start": 350.639,
    "duration": 6.441
  },
  {
    "text": "your fault.",
    "start": 353.6,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What's wrong?",
    "start": 357.199,
    "duration": 5.601
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's nothing. Thanks, friend.",
    "start": 359.84,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't dare tell him about how my",
    "start": 362.8,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "cowardice got my mother killed and my",
    "start": 365.12,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "father imprisoned. I thought he would",
    "start": 368.08,
    "duration": 5.679
  },
  {
    "text": "try and abandon me, too. Over the years,",
    "start": 370.479,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "however, as I grew older, my guilt grew,",
    "start": 373.759,
    "duration": 5.88
  },
  {
    "text": "too.",
    "start": 376.639,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "One day, I decided to tell the deer",
    "start": 381.52,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "everything. What? We have to do",
    "start": 384.24,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "something. You'll help me save my father",
    "start": 386.96,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "from that place? Of course. We're",
    "start": 390.08,
    "duration": 5.119
  },
  {
    "text": "guardians of the forest after all. But",
    "start": 392.479,
    "duration": 4.081
  },
  {
    "text": "my father,",
    "start": 395.199,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": ">> it's been so many years. I'm sure he",
    "start": 396.56,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "will have forgiven you by now. I wasn't",
    "start": 399.12,
    "duration": 6.4
  },
  {
    "text": "so sure, but the deer was insistent. So,",
    "start": 401.759,
    "duration": 6.321
  },
  {
    "text": "off we went back into the belly of the",
    "start": 405.52,
    "duration": 6.12
  },
  {
    "text": "beast, the frog kingdom.",
    "start": 408.08,
    "duration": 6.689
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 411.64,
    "duration": 3.129
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah, more visitors in my royal court.",
    "start": 415.12,
    "duration": 9.359
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a minute. Is that the owl prince? I",
    "start": 418.96,
    "duration": 7.92
  },
  {
    "text": "see you made a friend.",
    "start": 424.479,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes, we've come for my father. Release",
    "start": 426.88,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "him to me at once or suffer the",
    "start": 429.68,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "consequences.",
    "start": 431.44,
    "duration": 6.599
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I don't think so. Now,",
    "start": 432.72,
    "duration": 5.319
  },
  {
    "text": "that won't work this time.",
    "start": 448.08,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "What the?",
    "start": 451.52,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "You will pay for that.",
    "start": 454.08,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Find your father. I'll deal with the",
    "start": 456.72,
    "duration": 3.199
  },
  {
    "text": "toad.",
    "start": 459.039,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Thank you, my friend. Well, you want",
    "start": 459.919,
    "duration": 6.521
  },
  {
    "text": "some?",
    "start": 463.44,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Father.",
    "start": 471.759,
    "duration": 4.641
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Son, is that really you?",
    "start": 473.039,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes, father. I've come back for you.",
    "start": 476.4,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Stand back.",
    "start": 479.12,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I know it's taken me a long time to",
    "start": 481.36,
    "duration": 7.88
  },
  {
    "text": "return. I'm so sorry. I'm sorry, too.",
    "start": 483.28,
    "duration": 5.96
  },
  {
    "text": "You took everything from me.",
    "start": 490.16,
    "duration": 4.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I came to save you. Please stop this.",
    "start": 495.28,
    "duration": 6.199
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, please",
    "start": 507.12,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "stop. Stop calling me that. I'm not your",
    "start": 509.52,
    "duration": 5.999
  },
  {
    "text": "father. You're not my son. You're",
    "start": 512.8,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "nothing but a disappointment. And now",
    "start": 515.519,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "you will die.",
    "start": 518.24,
    "duration": 3.719
  },
  {
    "text": "Owl.",
    "start": 522.64,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Father.",
    "start": 525.36,
    "duration": 8.88
  },
  {
    "text": "He tried to but you killed him. You ra",
    "start": 526.88,
    "duration": 11.76
  },
  {
    "text": "friend please. I am not your friend.",
    "start": 534.24,
    "duration": 8.64
  },
  {
    "text": "From now on we are enemies.",
    "start": 538.64,
    "duration": 7.36
  },
  {
    "text": "You hear me dear monster?",
    "start": 542.88,
    "duration": 6.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Enemies.",
    "start": 546.0,
    "duration": 3.0
  }
]